{"tid":184262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網絡熱話:土地問題入門即見馬桶 網友：真正開放式","createTime":"2017-04-02T16:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T07:11:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de5d6be20d045cdfc51149ce8923ee700e4acefb","tid":184262,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.e-zone.com.hk/thumbs/735x420/1/channelnews/20170331122649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-zone.com.hk%2Fthumbs%2F735x420%2F1%2Fchannelnews%2F20170331122649.jpg&h=574852d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nshiuhk 三月 31, 2017 12:17<br />\n地少人多，土地問題一直沒有辦法解決。所以，不少樓盤都推出了各種稀奇古怪的超細上車盤。過往，香港就出現過超細長方形屋，坐上馬桶根本無法關門，引起網上不少討論。不過，都比不上以下這個奇葩設計。同樣是三尖八角的小型盤，這次竟然將馬桶直接放到大門旁邊，真正的開放式一人單位！<br />\n<br />\n這個位於東京新宿的租屋，可以説是應有盡有，9.22 平方米入面有一體式廚房連洗衣機，智能馬桶、浴室設備齊全。而且位置交通方便，離「東京 メトロ 東西線早稲田駅」只有 5 分鐘距離，十分方便。唯一奇怪的，就是馬桶的位置正正大門的旁邊。如果是一個人住，的確挺方便，急的話一入門口就可以上厠所。不過，開放式就有開放的問題。例如臭氣會聚在整間屋入面，朋友上來會覺得尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n這個租盤就月租 5.7 萬円（約 HKD $3990），整棟樓都只有 5 戶不怕嘈。如果香港出現這種租盤，大家又有沒有興趣呢？<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.e-zone.com.hk/upload/62427/jp1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-zone.com.hk%2Fupload%2F62427%2Fjp1.jpg&h=fa22cfa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.e-zone.com.hk/upload/62427/jp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-zone.com.hk%2Fupload%2F62427%2Fjp2.jpg&h=74adc846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.e-zone.com.hk/upload/62427/jp4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-zone.com.hk%2Fupload%2F62427%2Fjp4.jpg&h=b2c2c1c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.e-zone.com.hk/channelnews.php?id=23602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-zone.com.hk%2Fchannelnews.php%3Fid%3D23602&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=bb5abe1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.e-zone.com.hk/channelnews.php?id=23602</a>"},{"pid":"c525c09700dca0f2d6e060cce722750682c16917","tid":184262,"uid":71710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"點會on9到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb1e669aa68e20d19aed2d07c9d6fea39a96ef4","tid":184262,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:32:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e2fa35a4103f8c0ffedd51b7602e27dc0370eda","tid":184262,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:56:34.000Z","msg":"呢幢樓全部屋啲馬桶都係就咁擺喺度<br />\n有啲就擺喺煮食爐隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6acebd9e185a90531f576f6cc8b510d4267d117","tid":184262,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"睇黎要出街痾屎"},{"pid":"837ad9a1ed610f19d51d1520b506dc3fe0423324","tid":184262,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"起到咁都唔知為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef618cfd6db588ee2c7a2848993953641cf0afce","tid":184262,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T23:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f281d399bcb17e5c47eab138c11217b422b7a5","tid":184262,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T23:33:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個馬桶放第二度都可以諗計間個廁所出黎<br />\n放正門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間出走廊"},{"pid":"07fc5628ec80e7c00fb3314838c23c3e1900fa33","tid":184262,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"偉大既日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n創意無限"},{"pid":"b72d29858525257c6f85d7c1576b01a4c5c068e4","tid":184262,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2